	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2868653569" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2868653569" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Hey Marcelo,</p><p>Could you debug it by running <code>bin/console doctrine:schema:validate</code> command? And let me know its result. It shows whether you have any invalid mapping.</p><p>BTW, you probably use  `user` column name instead of `user_id` in some of your indexes or uniqueConstraints. Please, recheck that all your entities (not only Course entity) have `user_id` column name instead of `user` inside @ORM\Table() annotation. Actually, you have to check all the entities which have relation to the User entity.</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
