	                                <p>Hey Shairyar!</p><p>Hmm, I'm not sure. But! To find out, here's what I would do. Suppose that the persisted property on College for the image is called imagePath. First, I'd see if anything in College modifies the imagePath property other than setImagePath(). If anything else *does* modify imagePath, then temporarily comment that out and edit the College - see if the image is lost. Also, throw a new \Exception() in setImagePath() to see if something is calling it on College edit.</p><p>My guess is that you might be setting $this-&gt;imagePath = null; inside setLogo() or something similar, but I'm not sure :).</p><p>Cheers!</p>
